the truth,

81
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,280
would you've continued
to keep it from me?

82
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,320
I don't understand

83
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:27,080
why Lingyi
concealed the truth for you.

84
