I failed him.

90
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,120
If anything bad

91
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,040
happens to Lingyi

92
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,680
because of your doing,

93
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,160
I will never forgive you.

94
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,160
Why?

95
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:56,640
Why did you do this?

96
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,360
Why did you...

97
