News broke from the disaster-hit area.

101
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,080
Someone saw that

102
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,920
His Lordship died in a fire

103
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,840
to save the civilians.

104
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,360
Great Madam. Great Madam.

105
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,960
Mother.

106
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,400
-Your Ladyship.
-Your Ladyship.

107
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,360
-Great Madam.
-Mother.

108
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,920
-Great Madam. Wake up.
-Mother.

109
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,360
-Mother.
-Great Madam.

110
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,600
Great Madam.

111
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,520
-Mother.
-Mother.

112
