Your Ladyship.

114
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,640
Did he just say

115
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:34,480
His Lordship died?

116
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,030
Your Ladyship.

117
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,840
Your Ladyship.

118
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,280
Your Ladyship.

119
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,120
Your Ladyship.

120
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,880
-Your Ladyship.
-Your Ladyship.

121
00:08:59,040 --> 00:08:59,920
Your Ladyship.

122
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,200
Lingyi is a great martial artist.

123
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:19,080
He couldn't have died in a fire.

124
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:22,440
There must be something wrong.

125
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,040
The Ou familyhas had operations

126
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,360
in Shandong for so many years.

127
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,640
He must have killed Lingyi.

128
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,280
I'll settle accounts with him right now.

129
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,320
-Lingkuan.
-Stop.

130
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,080
The situation is unclear yet.

131
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,640
If His Lordship really died,

132
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,960
then the whole family depends on you.

133
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,800
If misfortune strikes you

134
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:36,360
as well,

135
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,680
what will happen to the Xu family?

136
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,560
Lingkuan.

137
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,400
I know

138
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,120
you and His Lordship
love each other as brothers.

139
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,280
But you need to think for the benefits

140
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,840
of me and the baby.

141
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,840
I'm useless.

142
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,480
I know someone murdered Lingyi.

143
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,480
