Yi'er.

145
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,180
Great Madam.

146
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:03,960
-Mother.
-Mother.

147
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,160
Is my Yi'er

148
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,840
really gone?

149
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,120
Will he never

150
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,280
come back?

151
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,560
My Yi'er

152
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:24,800
worked so hard

153
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,480
for his country and family.

154
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,480
But he didn't

155
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,800
even get to see his family

