166
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:15,240
My son was a great martial artist.

167
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:19,120
If she hadn't stabbed him,

168
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:27,240
he wouldn't have died in a fire.

169
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,800
Where is Shiyi?

170
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,680
Where is Shiyi?

171
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,560
Go.

172
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:44,280
Bring her to me.

173
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,760
Mother.

174
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,040
Please don't be emotional.

175
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,840
Calm down, alright?

176
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,640
She conspired with our enemy

177
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,080
and showed her heartless nature.

178
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,920
She is not to be tolerated.

179
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:07,040
I want her to pay
for his death with her life.

180
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,000
Mother.

181
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,920
I'm also mad at Shiyi

182
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,480
for stabbing Lingyi.

183
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,960
But I know her well enough

184
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,600
to assert that she would never

185
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,120
maliciously conspire with our enemy.

186
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:22,040
There must be something wrong.

187
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,440
Mother.

188
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,200
Don't do anything impulsive.

189
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,680
Yeah, Mother.

190
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,120
I know you want Shiyi
to pay with her life,

191
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,480
but you can't accuse her
of conspiring with our enemy

192
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,280
without any evidence.

193
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,840
How will we explain things

194
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,480
to the Luo family?

195
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,480
Explain?

196
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:41,120
The Luo family should
explain things to me.

197
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,840
Every generation of the Xu family

198
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,640
serves in the military.

199
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:52,240
Family rules are
as serious as military rules.

200
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,240
She injured the head of the family,

201
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:58,000
which is like killing
the commander before a battle.

202
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:02,040
I want her to pay
for his death with her life.

203
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:09,920
Your Ladyship,

204
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,440
what are you doing?

205
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,320
He survived the perilous battlefield

206
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,720
and came back.

207
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,840
I don't believe he died like this.

208
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:18,600
Your Ladyship.

209
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,840
Your Ladyship, calm down.

210
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,400
Your Ladyship,
Shandong is so far from us.

211
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,040
You can't just head there

212
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:23,240
as a woman.

213
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,600
I must see for myself.

214
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,080
I don't believe he is dead.

215
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,160
