216
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,080
his body will be sent back

217
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,800
before long.

218
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,560
I don't believe it.

219
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,040
-Your Ladyship.
-Your Ladyship.

220
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:41,960
Shiyi.

221
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,680
You must leave as soon as possible.

222
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,400
Mother broke down

223
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,440
after she learned of His Lordship's death.

224
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,880
She wants you to pay
for his death with your life.

225
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:49,840
She can't solely blame Her Ladyship

226
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,600
for the death of His Lordship.

227
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,680
Mother has lost

228
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:53,880
her husband and her son.

229
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,880
She barely survived those tragedies.

230
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,600
Now she is old,

231
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:58,640
she can't take

232
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,840
another loss.

233
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:01,560
It's inevitable that
she'll take extreme measures.

234
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,720
Shiyi,

235
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,680
since His Lordship covered up your action,

236
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:05,480
I'm sure

237
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,920
there's an explanation for it.

238
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,080
Right now, Mother has lost

239
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:09,520
her head.

240
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,520
You need to leave

241
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,640
and hide out.

242
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,400
Dongqing, the Divorce Agreement.

243
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:17,880
Once we show Great Madam

244
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:18,560
the Divorce Agreement,

245
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,480
she won't be able

246
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,440
to punish you.

247
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,560
Now I see.

248
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:22,600
His Lordship must have

249
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,400
foreseen this.

250
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,200
So he wrote a Divorce Agreement

251
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,400
(Divorce Agreement)
to protect you.

252
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,640
You're saying His Lordship

253
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,240
wrote a Divorce Agreement
before he left?

254
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,400
Why did you keep it?

255
