273
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,600
I don't need your opinion

274
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,840
on this matter.

275
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,520
Luo Shiyi,

276
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:54,800
are you convinced?

277
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,400
I treated His Lordship unfairly.

278
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,600
I deserve punishment.

279
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,560
Unfairly?

280
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:11,560
Lingyi loved you so much.

281
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:13,200
But you stabbed him.

282
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:16,000
